1
00:00:02,045 --> 00:00:08,385
Krishna who is acarcan, he has magnetic attraction.

2
00:00:08,385 --> 00:00:12,305
Krishna. The devotees sometimes they call him Karshni.

3
00:00:12,305 --> 00:00:15,392
So Krishna, Madan Mohan,

4
00:00:15,392 --> 00:00:21,261
Cupid who is bewildering everyone with his seductive charm,

5
00:00:21,261 --> 00:00:26,194
Krishna is Madan Mohan, puts cupid into a state of bewilderment.

6
00:00:26,194 --> 00:00:29,762

7
00:00:29,762 --> 00:00:32,824
But Radharani the ultimate personification,

8
00:00:32,824 --> 00:00:40,567
devotion personified to its extreme, to its limits,

9
00:00:40,567 --> 00:00:43,708
prema rasa sima

10
00:00:43,708 --> 00:00:50,252
She is Madan Mohan Mohini, she can attract Krishna.

11
00:00:50,252 --> 00:00:58,419
Hare Krishna means also what sometimes Krishna is told as Hari.

12
00:00:58,419 --> 00:01:02,308
One meaning who steals away.

13
00:01:02,308 --> 00:01:12,836
But Hare, Hare Krishna, Guru Maharaj said, Radharani she can steal the mind of Krishna.

14
00:01:12,836 --> 00:01:23,412
So Gurudev like to quote this one sloka where a devotee is noticing

15
00:01:23,412 --> 00:01:32,626
that Krishna's mind has been stolen, he's absent his mind,

16
00:01:32,626 --> 00:01:36,171
like we are saying Radharani can steel the mind of Krishna

17
00:01:36,171 --> 00:01:40,421
with her manohar ladus, or divine serving mood.

18
00:01:40,421 --> 00:01:50,254
So he noticed Krishna is lost his mind and in this sloka

19
00:01:50,254 --> 00:01:54,149
is offering his mind to him.

20
00:01:54,149 --> 00:02:00,672
I see you've lost your mind, so I'm offering mine to you.

21
00:02:00,672 --> 00:02:07,840
And one devotee asked Srila Guru Maharaj, he said,

22
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:14,127
"And what did Krishna say?"

23
00:02:14,127 --> 00:02:18,132
It's one of his divine sloka concepts

24
00:02:18,132 --> 00:02:20,718

25
00:02:20,718 --> 00:02:27,016
"Then what did Krishna say?"

26
00:02:27,016 --> 00:02:31,854
to the devotee offering his mind

27
00:02:31,854 --> 00:02:36,709
Guru Maharaj said, "Krishna said

28
00:02:36,709 --> 00:02:41,846
"Oh what little mind I have left, you want to take that?"

